(23, 'Install netdata - realtime monitoring system di Ubuntu 14.04', '2016-04-05', '<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Net<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">D</span>ata adalah daemon app yang mengumpulkan data <span class=\"\">secara realtime</span> (per detik) dan menyajikan <span class=\"\">sebuah situs</span> web untuk melihat dan <span class=\"\">menganalisis mereka</span>. Presentasi juga <span class=\"\">real-time</span> dan penuh grafik interaktif yang tepat <span class=\"\">membuat semua</span> nilai yang dikumpulkan.</span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Aplikasi Ini telah dirancang untuk diinstal pada setiap sistem, tanpa mengganggu aplikasi yang berjalan di atasnya: &nbsp;</span></span><br /><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Ini hanya akan menggunakan beberapa siklus CPU cadang (<a href=\"https://github.com/firehol/netdata/wiki/Performance\" target=\"_blank\">cek</a><a href=\"https://github.com/firehol/netdata/wiki/Performance\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><a href=\"https://github.com/firehol/netdata/wiki/Performance\" target=\"_blank\">Performance</a>).&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Ini akan menggunakan memori Anda menginginkannya memiliki (<a href=\"https://github.com/firehol/netdata/wiki/Memory-Requirements\" target=\"_blank\">periksa Persyaratan Memory</a>). &nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Setelah dimulai dan sementara berjalan, itu tidak menggunakan disk I / O, selain penebangan kayu (<a href=\"https://github.com/firehol/netdata/wiki/Log-Files\" target=\"_blank\">periksa Log Files</a>). Tentu saja menghemat DB untuk disk ketika keluar dan beban itu kembali ketika mulai.</span></span></li></ul><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rRxojsSPX7k/VwvnDww7yuI/AAAAAAAADDE/xsn1XDgT-M4YWkbd4DbxL7uT2L_RSv6QA/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2016-04-12%2B01%253A03%253A26.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"179\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rRxojsSPX7k/VwvnDww7yuI/AAAAAAAADDE/xsn1XDgT-M4YWkbd4DbxL7uT2L_RSv6QA/s320/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2016-04-12%2B01%253A03%253A26.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Anda  dapat menggunakannya untuk memantau semua sistem dan aplikasi. Itu akan  berjalan pada Linux PC, server atau perangkat embedded.</span></span><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Keluar dari kotak, ia datang dengan plugin yang mengumpulkan metrik sistem kunci dan metrik aplikasi populer.</span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Web-Resmi Dari NetData ada di GitHubnya : <a href=\"https://github.com/firehol/netdata\">https://github.com/firehol/netdata&nbsp;</a></span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Dokumentasi Resmi Installasinya : <a href=\"https://github.com/firehol/netdata/wiki/Installation\">https://github.com/firehol/netdata/wiki/Installation</a></span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Langkah-Langkah Installasi :</span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">1. Masuk Ke Terminal dan Masuk Sebagai SUper User (#) den<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">gan perintah&nbsp;</span></span></span><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">$sudo su</span></span></span></blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">2. Masukan Perintah dibawah ini untuk mengistall beberapa aplikasi depensi atau kebutuhan netdata secara manual, dengan perintah</span></span><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">#apt-get install zlib1g-dev gcc make git autoconf autogen automake pkg-config</span></span></blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">3. Clone Bash Installer dari gitnya dengan perintah&nbsp;</span></span><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">#git clone https://github.com/firehol/netdata.git --depth=1</span></span></blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">4. Masuk ke folder netdata yang telah anda clone dengan perintah&nbsp;</span></span><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">#cd netdata</span></span></blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">5. Eksekusi bash installer dengan perintah&nbsp;</span></span><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">#./netdata-installer.sh</span></span></blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span title=\"The script netdata-installer.sh will build netdata and install it to your system.  \">Script netdata-installer.sh akan membangun netdata dan menginstalnya pada sistem Anda.<br /></span><span title=\"If you don\'t want to install it on the default directories, you can run the installer like this: ./netdata-installer.sh --install /opt.\">Jika   Anda tidak ingin menginstalnya pada direktori default, Anda dapat   menjalankan installer seperti ini: ./netdata-installer.sh --install  /opt. </span><span title=\"This one will install netdata in /opt/netdata.  \">yang satu ini akan menginstal netdata di /opt/netdata.<br /></span><span title=\"Once the installer completes, the file /etc/netdata/netdata.conf will be created (if you changed the installation directory, the configuration will appear in that directory too).  \">Setelah installer selesai, file /etc/netdata/netdata.conf akan dibuat   (jika Anda mengubah direktori instalasi, konfigurasi akan muncul di   direktori itu juga).<br /></span><span title=\"You can edit this file to set options.\">Anda dapat mengedit file ini untuk mengatur opsi. </span><span title=\"One common option to tweak is history, which controls the size of the memory database netdata will use.\">Salah satu pilihan yang umum untuk men-tweak adalah history, yang mengontrol ukuran database memori netdata akan menggunakan. </span><span title=\"By default is 3600 seconds (an hour of data at the charts) which makes netdata use about 10-15MB of RAM (depending on the number of charts detected on your system).\">Secara   default adalah 3600 detik (satu jam dari data pada grafik) yang  membuat  netdata menggunakan sekitar 10-15MB RAM (tergantung pada jumlah  grafik  terdeteksi pada sistem Anda). </span><span title=\"Check Memory Requirements.  \">Periksa Persyaratan Memory.<br /></span><span title=\"To apply the changes you made, you have to restart netdata.\">Untuk menerapkan perubahan yang Anda buat, Anda harus me-restart netdata.</span></span></span></span> <br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><br /></span></span> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">6.  Jika Sudah Selesai maka anda dapat langsung menjalankan netdata dengan  perintah #netdata , lalu setelah itu anda dapat membuka web browser dan  mengakses netdata melalui port 19999 , sebagai contoh  http://localhost:19999 , seperti <span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">gambar dibawah ini</span></span></span><br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rRxojsSPX7k/VwvnDww7yuI/AAAAAAAADDE/xsn1XDgT-M4YWkbd4DbxL7uT2L_RSv6QA/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2016-04-12%2B01%253A03%253A26.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rRxojsSPX7k/VwvnDww7yuI/AAAAAAAADDE/xsn1XDgT-M4YWkbd4DbxL7uT2L_RSv6QA/s400/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2016-04-12%2B01%253A03%253A26.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><br /></span></span> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">netdata  tidak langsung berjalan ketika komputer/server anda hidup maka anda  haru menjalankanya secara manual dengan perintah #netdata atau jika anda  ingin aplikasi ini berjalan secara otomatis di server anda ketika  dihidupkan-ulang maka anda dapat mengikuti langkah berikut , #nano  /etc/rc.local , masukan \"/usr/sbin/netdata\"diata exit 0 lal<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">u ke<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">luar dan simpan dengan cara tekan ctrl+x kemudian y lalu tekan enter , maka secara otomatis netdata akan <span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">hid<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">up ketika kompu<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">ter anda dihidup<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">kan ulang</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><br /></blockquote>', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2016/04/install-netdata-realtime-monitoring.html', 1),
(24, 'Mengaktifkan mod_rewrite apache2 di Ubuntu 14.04/LinuxMint 17.3', '2016-03-23', 'Sebuah<b> rewrite engine</b> adalah komponen perangkat lunak yang melakukan penulisan ulang pada Uniform Resource Locator , memodifikasi penampilan mereka. Modifikasi ini disebut URL menulis ulang. Ini adalah cara menerapkan pemetaan URL atau routing dalam sebuah aplikasi web . Mesin biasanya komponen dari web server atau aplikasi web framework . URL ditulis ulang (kadang-kadang dikenal sebagai pendek, cantik atau mewah URL, search engine friendly - URL SEF, atau siput ) digunakan untuk menyediakan lebih pendek dan lebih relevan tampak link ke halaman web. Teknik ini menambahkan lapisan abstraksi antara file yang digunakan untuk menghasilkan halaman web dan URL yang disajikan kepada dunia luar.<br /><br />Langkah-langkah :<br />1.Buka Terminal Di Ubuntu/Linux anda masukan perintah berikut seperti gambar dibawah<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">$sudo a2enmod rewrite </blockquote><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ct28scXYDXo/VvJWVwTyJTI/AAAAAAAAC7U/r5zpVbpiRAghY_Id2dNWL8U2qQ0HKnRSQ/s1600/1.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"49\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ct28scXYDXo/VvJWVwTyJTI/AAAAAAAAC7U/r5zpVbpiRAghY_Id2dNWL8U2qQ0HKnRSQ/s320/1.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br />2.edit file sites apache dengan memasukan perintah dibawah<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">$sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/000-default.conf</blockquote><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NqHImCEl_HE/VvJWVxfvNhI/AAAAAAAAC7M/di9tI8bZcNksVBKYa9_2hjdzbftphXOPw/s1600/2.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NqHImCEl_HE/VvJWVxfvNhI/AAAAAAAAC7M/di9tI8bZcNksVBKYa9_2hjdzbftphXOPw/s320/2.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>Masukan Beberapa konfigurasi dibawah seperti gambar<br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <directory html=\"\" var=\"\" www=\"\"><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Options Indexes FollowSymLinks MultiViews<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AllowOverride All<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Order allow,deny<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; allow from all<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </directory></blockquote><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4kU7_VEUwkM/VvJWV1QSFWI/AAAAAAAAC7Q/4uWx27rmM98NYwRTX_hT0-Phivi8wRr4Q/s1600/3.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"204\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4kU7_VEUwkM/VvJWV1QSFWI/AAAAAAAAC7Q/4uWx27rmM98NYwRTX_hT0-Phivi8wRr4Q/s320/3.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br />3.Reload dan Restart Service apache2 anda dengan perintah dibawah maka akan menampilkan hasil seperti gambar dibawah<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">$sudo service apache2 reload<br /><br />$sudo service apache2 restart</blockquote><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VsJBHungBiw/VvJWW1kqw1I/AAAAAAAAC7Y/o49d6dkBMjUQbClsiKI6Ybv3sH_rbUd3Q/s1600/4.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"52\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VsJBHungBiw/VvJWW1kqw1I/AAAAAAAAC7Y/o49d6dkBMjUQbClsiKI6Ybv3sH_rbUd3Q/s320/4.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br />4. Anda dapat memeriksa apakah mod_rewrite sudah berjalan atau belum dengan membuka phpinfo(); ,&nbsp; maka akan muncul seperti gambar dibawah ini<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9PjD6zntSRA/VvJWW--7pYI/AAAAAAAAC7c/HeOKsmwO5kYdMZsrtlJMe3JXMgtF4VMTw/s1600/5.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"272\" src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9PjD6zntSRA/VvJWW--7pYI/AAAAAAAAC7c/HeOKsmwO5kYdMZsrtlJMe3JXMgtF4VMTw/s320/5.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2016/03/mengaktifkan-modrewrite-apache2-di.html', 1),
(25, 'Mengistall LAMP Server di Raspbian Jessie - RaspberryPi 2 B+', '2016-03-12', '<b>LAMP</b> adalah istilah yang merupakan singkatan dari <a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a>, <a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Apache HTTP Server\">Apache</a>, <a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"MySQL\">MySQL</a> dan <a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Perl\">Perl</a>/<a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"PHP\">PHP</a>/<a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Phyton\">Phyton</a>. Merupakan sebuah paket <a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Perangkat lunak bebas\">perangkat lunak bebas</a> yang digunakan untuk menjalankan sebuah aplikasi secara lengkap.<br />Komponen-komponen dari LAMP:<br /><ul><li><b>L</b>inux â€“ <a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Sistem operasi\">sistem operasi</a></li><li><b>A</b>pache HTTP Server â€“ <a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Web server\">web server</a></li><li><b>M</b>ariaDB atau <a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"MySQL\"><b>M</b>ySQL</a> â€“ sistem basis data</li><li><b>P</b>HP atau <a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Perl\"><b>P</b>erl</a> atau <a class=\"mw-disambig\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/null\" title=\"Python\"><b>P</b>ython</a> â€“ bahasa pemrograman yang dipakai</li></ul>&nbsp;Berikut cara mengistall lamp di raspberrypi :<br /><br />1. Masuk Ke Raspi anda buka terminal (menu &gt; terminal /ctrl + alt + t) dan masukan perintah :<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">sudo apt-get install apache2</blockquote><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-n3Y7PzbQo9k/VvYe9ijBNQI/AAAAAAAAC8M/cukzINdiJVUJNSqrXTey8CpVYn_ncHlRQ/s1600/1.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"297\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-n3Y7PzbQo9k/VvYe9ijBNQI/AAAAAAAAC8M/cukzINdiJVUJNSqrXTey8CpVYn_ncHlRQ/s400/1.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tekan Enter Untuk Y besar</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br />setelah selesai silahkan buka web browser anda dan masukan alamat ke localhost maka akan keluar seperti gambar dibawah ini maka service web server anda sudah berjalan<br /><br /><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-2WEJrjgGWb0/VvYfNngXbGI/AAAAAAAAC8Q/04owFaxaQNQywbnwiKqtNhvWFYl2sW2VA/s1600/2.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-2WEJrjgGWb0/VvYfNngXbGI/AAAAAAAAC8Q/04owFaxaQNQywbnwiKqtNhvWFYl2sW2VA/s400/2.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">service web server anda sudah berjalan</td></tr></tbody></table>2.kembali ke terminal dan masukan perintah<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">sudo apt-get install libapache2-mod-php5 php5 php5-mcrypt php5-cli php5-json php5-cgi php5-common php5-curl php5-dbg php5-dev php5-gd</blockquote><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_a-gI5Ylv-0/VvYgKjsEzTI/AAAAAAAAC8c/6mrsRPoBI3QS4zuboughMmPp_f1LPiEkA/s1600/3.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"297\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_a-gI5Ylv-0/VvYgKjsEzTI/AAAAAAAAC8c/6mrsRPoBI3QS4zuboughMmPp_f1LPiEkA/s400/3.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tekan Enter Untuk Y Besar</td><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td></tr></tbody></table>jika sudah anda dapat membuat file phpinfo() di document root (/var/www/html)<br />mengikuti perintah yang ada pada gambar dibawah ini<br /><br /><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PU63LxdIM04/VvYgpIo3YzI/AAAAAAAAC8g/YjU0zNJCppAUBDDfKsUKif2BkfgcJ9MPg/s1600/5.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"52\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PU63LxdIM04/VvYgpIo3YzI/AAAAAAAAC8g/YjU0zNJCppAUBDDfKsUKif2BkfgcJ9MPg/s400/5.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">sudo nano /var/www/html/test.php</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AohhC0L1Qs8/VvYgpEpWcbI/AAAAAAAAC8k/UiQI7LHUYBM6Z9PeswxzBTWXbMUtBnvrg/s1600/6.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"298\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AohhC0L1Qs8/VvYgpEpWcbI/AAAAAAAAC8k/UiQI7LHUYBM6Z9PeswxzBTWXbMUtBnvrg/s400/6.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><br />anda dapat menuliskan isi file seperti gambar dibawah kemudian anda simpan dengan cara menekan ctrl+x kemudian tekan y tekan enter <br /><br /><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-MjSmP9hE4Ig/VvYgpWWlY5I/AAAAAAAAC8o/Ge0VTXGuF0wB0OqiCZq5bhL2yY8IZYWbw/s1600/7.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"298\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-MjSmP9hE4Ig/VvYgpWWlY5I/AAAAAAAAC8o/Ge0VTXGuF0wB0OqiCZq5bhL2yY8IZYWbw/s400/7.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">PHP anda sudah berjalan di webserver</td><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></td></tr></tbody></table>3. install MySql Server dan PhpMyAdmin, kembali ke terminal masukan perintah berikut sesuai dengan gambar dibawah ini<br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">sudo apt-get install php5-mysql mysql-server mysql-client phpmyadmin</blockquote><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-x8QzMS-ntVo/VvYhvlJleGI/AAAAAAAAC9M/pNBUZUUdIGwXJcVjCbkaPPQNV9W3QMCvg/s1600/8.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-x8QzMS-ntVo/VvYhvlJleGI/AAAAAAAAC9M/pNBUZUUdIGwXJcVjCbkaPPQNV9W3QMCvg/s400/8.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tekan Enter Untuk Y Besar</td></tr></tbody></table>&nbsp;setelah beberapa saat anda akan diminta memesukan password untuk mysql root user<br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-cQfBoS_zf_w/VvYhwFTBFGI/AAAAAAAAC9Q/cEfWfNEp1pwr4EpAXJv3YCzA0iMf2QdDw/s1600/9.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"298\" src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-cQfBoS_zf_w/VvYhwFTBFGI/AAAAAAAAC9Q/cEfWfNEp1pwr4EpAXJv3YCzA0iMf2QdDw/s400/9.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><br />anda akan diminta memasukan password sekali lagi <br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6EUcm34nAq4/VvYhuclXkcI/AAAAAAAAC84/NjjeIBwFGlwu4xZin-HyystOXCDkPWCGw/s1600/10.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6EUcm34nAq4/VvYhuclXkcI/AAAAAAAAC84/NjjeIBwFGlwu4xZin-HyystOXCDkPWCGw/s400/10.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>&nbsp;pilih apache2 dengan menekan tombol spasi lalu tekan enter<br /><br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-tMbaZtCEduU/VvYhujgf_bI/AAAAAAAAC9A/hEyc6NBqBYA34P2C-Xl5Va97IKsTZ1HOQ/s1600/11.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-tMbaZtCEduU/VvYhujgf_bI/AAAAAAAAC9A/hEyc6NBqBYA34P2C-Xl5Va97IKsTZ1HOQ/s400/11.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><br />akan muncul pertanyaan seperti gambar dibawah pilih NO <br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0fmcKGL0x2I/VvYhumxBwaI/AAAAAAAAC88/dVKI56Iw6qw4g2YUU7HnbTqbmAF__8vew/s1600/12.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"301\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0fmcKGL0x2I/VvYhumxBwaI/AAAAAAAAC88/dVKI56Iw6qw4g2YUU7HnbTqbmAF__8vew/s400/12.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><br />&nbsp;setelah installasi selesai maka anda dapat langsung memcobanya dengan membuka phpmyadmin dengan membuka web browser dan membuka \"localhost/phpmyadmin\" lalu anda dapat login dengan username root dan password yang anda masukan tadi<br /><br /><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-WUMB8BNNeBs/VvYhvW0k3sI/AAAAAAAAC9E/z_2XjvsqkroKXKqlGOYs9VKG8qHLcrVhw/s1600/13.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-WUMB8BNNeBs/VvYhvW0k3sI/AAAAAAAAC9E/z_2XjvsqkroKXKqlGOYs9VKG8qHLcrVhw/s400/13.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tampilan Login</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cejI7xM6aLc/VvYhvZxAUhI/AAAAAAAAC9I/pPAJ9XVvJTM7Bg7XtDDifDf2p5TVk-cww/s1600/14.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cejI7xM6aLc/VvYhvZxAUhI/AAAAAAAAC9I/pPAJ9XVvJTM7Bg7XtDDifDf2p5TVk-cww/s400/14.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tampilan Setelah Login</td></tr></tbody></table>', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2016/03/mengistall-lamp-server-di-raspbian.html', 1),
(26, 'Mengatasi ERROR pada Apache2 di Ubuntu \"Set NameServer\"', '2016-02-17', 'Pesan Error yang muncul jika kita memasukan perintah untuk merestart service apache pada ubuntu 14.04 LTS/Linux Mint 17.x<br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-jNVWjejAuRQ/VsQBVu3Aw-I/AAAAAAAAC64/4NKhIKD9Rqg/s1600/Name-Server.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"46\" src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-jNVWjejAuRQ/VsQBVu3Aw-I/AAAAAAAAC64/4NKhIKD9Rqg/s400/Name-Server.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Restarting web server apache2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AH00558: apache2: Could not reliably determine the server\'s fully qualified domain name, using 127.0.0.1. Set the \'ServerName\' directive globally to suppress this message<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [ OK ]<br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br />&nbsp;Cara Mengatasi Error Tersebut dengan langkah-langkah sebagai berikut :<br />1. Buka terminal<br /><br />2. masukan Perintah<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $echo \"ServerName localhost\" | sudo tee /etc/apache2/conf-available/fqdn.conf &amp;&amp; sudo a2enconf fqdn<br /><br />&nbsp;perintah diatas digunakan untuk membuat file /etc/apache2/conf-available/fqdn.conf dan mengisi ServerName anda ke localhost kemudian mengaktifkan konfigurasi yang anda buat ke service apache2<br /><br /><br />3. Kemudian reload dan restart service apache2 anda dengan perintah<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #service apache2 reload &amp;&amp; service apache2 restart<br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2ft-w_IP3RE/VsQBaHWim9I/AAAAAAAAC68/-Dp3Ptp94XM/s1600/OK.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"18\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2ft-w_IP3RE/VsQBaHWim9I/AAAAAAAAC68/-Dp3Ptp94XM/s400/OK.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><br />Sumber : https://help.ubuntu.com/community/ApacheMySQLPHP', '', 1),
(27, 'Mengistall Rasbian Jessie Di RasberryPI2B+ Melalui Ubuntu 14.04/LinuMint 17.3', '2016-01-20', '1. Masukan CardReader yang sudah anda pasang dengan memori card yang akan digunakan untuk raspi jika sudah maka lepaskan semua perangkat penyimpanan yang menempel seperti flashdisk/harddisk external agar anda tidak bingun, pastikan di komputer/laptop anda hanya ada harddisk internal dan memori untuk raspi , masukan perintah dibawah ini agar anda tau dimana link dev perangkat memori raspi anda<br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">$sudo fdisk -l</blockquote><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-rk87giLcAIs/VvJw_HP70FI/AAAAAAAAC7w/FE345bCKoQg_Nwv5J6IMuwq4k2ZwNVu1g/s1600/1.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"228\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-rk87giLcAIs/VvJw_HP70FI/AAAAAAAAC7w/FE345bCKoQg_Nwv5J6IMuwq4k2ZwNVu1g/s320/1.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br />maka anda akan mengetuhi link dev perangkat anda seperti yang saya tandai pada gambar diatas terdapat pada \"/dev/sdb\" , umount dulu perangkat tersebut dengan perintah<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">$sudo umount /dev/sdb1</blockquote><br />2.Pastikan anda sudah memiliki raspbian jika belum anda dapat mengunduhnya <a href=\"https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/raspbian/\" target=\"_blank\">disini</a> <br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><a href=\"https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/raspbian/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/raspbian/ &nbsp;</a> </blockquote><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-w9dA6DRptG4/VvJw-5wRkhI/AAAAAAAAC7s/s61Cy7WFD8AlpF54bFoKz1ekV3RxNHclw/s1600/2.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"182\" src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-w9dA6DRptG4/VvJw-5wRkhI/AAAAAAAAC7s/s61Cy7WFD8AlpF54bFoKz1ekV3RxNHclw/s320/2.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br />jika anda sudah memiliki iso tersebut anda dapat berpindah directory kesana<br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Pn6Oweq4rPc/VvJw_KkxjRI/AAAAAAAAC70/FqDEoL6qRT89P3lt4uVQGBlxlPJjOUDhA/s1600/3.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"228\" src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Pn6Oweq4rPc/VvJw_KkxjRI/AAAAAAAAC70/FqDEoL6qRT89P3lt4uVQGBlxlPJjOUDhA/s320/3.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br />3. untuk mengistall raspbian anda hanya perlu memasukan perintah , seperti gambar dibawah ini<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">$dd bs=4M if=2016-02-09-raspbian-jessie.img of=/dev/sdb</blockquote><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-rfYRD1BNbEk/VvJw_yO8A_I/AAAAAAAAC74/gi2ffGuQPO4c4gsFgIpDnh8oNGyOSv73A/s1600/4.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"16\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-rfYRD1BNbEk/VvJw_yO8A_I/AAAAAAAAC74/gi2ffGuQPO4c4gsFgIpDnh8oNGyOSv73A/s320/4.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br />waktu yang dibutuhkan cukup lama tidak ada progress atau yang lainnya jadi anda harus menunggu dengan sabar<br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-oQ_TH493JuQ/VvJw_w4Mm2I/AAAAAAAAC78/0OZYXKUX_40BL7FY3Ns9VMJnheczXRLAA/s1600/5.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"50\" src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-oQ_TH493JuQ/VvJw_w4Mm2I/AAAAAAAAC78/0OZYXKUX_40BL7FY3Ns9VMJnheczXRLAA/s320/5.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br />', '', 1),
(28, 'Langkah-Langkah Mengistall PROXMOX', '2016-01-14', '1. Siapkan Installer Proxmox baik melalui CD/USB Flash<br />2. Setup BIOS , atur dan sesuaikan tanggal , waktu dan pastikan Intel/AMD V - Virtualization Technology [enable]<br />3. Boot Bios Ke Installer Anda<br />4. Akan Muncul Seperti gambar dibawah ini , pilih \"Install ...\" dengan menekan enter<br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NUuj78pJoio/VphhJzmGcRI/AAAAAAAAC4o/OOqToqkujX4/s1600/1.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"251\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NUuj78pJoio/VphhJzmGcRI/AAAAAAAAC4o/OOqToqkujX4/s400/1.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>5. Klik \"I agree\"<br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ub-spO7ORvQ/VphhKjhwFvI/AAAAAAAAC44/AUsu4Piq_Ks/s1600/2.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ub-spO7ORvQ/VphhKjhwFvI/AAAAAAAAC44/AUsu4Piq_Ks/s400/2.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>6. Pilih Harddisk Yang digunakan Klik \"Next\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-aavRZk5CcCY/VphhK4-jrII/AAAAAAAAC40/is_eroqRMtE/s1600/3.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-aavRZk5CcCY/VphhK4-jrII/AAAAAAAAC40/is_eroqRMtE/s400/3.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>7.Pilih Negara Dan Zone Waktu Klik \"Next\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JqNbdGiaILE/VphhLHotTJI/AAAAAAAAC48/HBkIOpV5sMM/s1600/4.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JqNbdGiaILE/VphhLHotTJI/AAAAAAAAC48/HBkIOpV5sMM/s400/4.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>8. Masukan Root Password Proxmox anda dan juga email anda Klik \"next\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WnftQ8OeehI/VphhLh7panI/AAAAAAAAC5A/JBaAufM35S4/s1600/5.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WnftQ8OeehI/VphhLh7panI/AAAAAAAAC5A/JBaAufM35S4/s400/5.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>9. Masukan hostname seperti \"proxmox.net.id\" dan atur ip address, subnet, gateway dan dns sever anda seperti contoh gambar dibawah, klik \"Next\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DM18OFjVte8/VphhL6J4Z4I/AAAAAAAAC5I/SDfV0iXJp4Q/s1600/6.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DM18OFjVte8/VphhL6J4Z4I/AAAAAAAAC5I/SDfV0iXJp4Q/s400/6.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>10. tunggu Installasi sampai Selesai<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oi9ogdFzQNk/VphhMKTmmKI/AAAAAAAAC5M/SJqGfxbzbq4/s1600/7.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"179\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oi9ogdFzQNk/VphhMKTmmKI/AAAAAAAAC5M/SJqGfxbzbq4/s320/7.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RCHPedKCrC8/VphhMlRv_1I/AAAAAAAAC5U/vIqMEa23E_Q/s1600/9.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"179\" src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RCHPedKCrC8/VphhMlRv_1I/AAAAAAAAC5U/vIqMEa23E_Q/s320/9.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>11. Klik \"Reboot\" dan lepaskan Installer anda <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4iXHbZjvu4U/VphhJrQGFaI/AAAAAAAAC4s/JAY40S7kWMQ/s1600/10.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4iXHbZjvu4U/VphhJrQGFaI/AAAAAAAAC4s/JAY40S7kWMQ/s400/10.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>Tampilan setelah terintall<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-gKwZ9ajSPeg/VphhJiVGfaI/AAAAAAAAC4k/T2BL8unaJ2k/s1600/11.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"220\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-gKwZ9ajSPeg/VphhJiVGfaI/AAAAAAAAC4k/T2BL8unaJ2k/s400/11.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>Buka Laptop Anda Dan anda dapat langsung mengkonfigurasi nya melalui web dengan memasukan alamat proxmox anda <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hdtQQDhVLwo/VphhXLBuuqI/AAAAAAAAC58/3E1zoG8tOcA/s1600/1_pre.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"221\" src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hdtQQDhVLwo/VphhXLBuuqI/AAAAAAAAC58/3E1zoG8tOcA/s400/1_pre.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><br />', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2016/01/langkah-langkah-mengistall-proxmox.html', 1),
(29, 'Mengenal rsync ( fast  and  extraordinarily  versatile file copying tool )', '2015-08-27', '<span class=\"notranslate\"><b>rsync</b> adalah utilitas banyak digunakan untuk menyimpan salinan dari file pada dua sistem komputer yang sama.<a href=\"https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=id&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.co.id&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rsync&amp;usg=ALkJrhhaCvu5VrODo4ydpkK3h4Zu7kPp1Q#cite_note-Sayood-3\"><sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-Sayood_3-0\"></sup></a> Hal ini umumnya ditemukan pada Unix-seperti sistem dan fungsi baik sebagai sinkronisasi file dan transfer file Program.</span><br /><span class=\"notranslate\"> The algoritma rsync, jenis delta encoding, digunakan untuk meminimalkan penggunaan jaringan. Zlib dapat digunakan untuk kompresi tambahan, dan SSH atau stunnel dapat digunakan untuk keamanan data.</span><br /><br /><span class=\"notranslate\"> rsync biasanya digunakan untuk melakukan sinkronisasi file dan direktori antara dua sistem yang berbeda.</span> <span class=\"notranslate\"> </span><br /><a name=\'more\'></a>Sebagai contoh, jika perintah<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><span class=\"notranslate\">&nbsp;<code>rsync local-file user@remote-host:remote-file</code>&nbsp;</span></blockquote><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\">dijalankan, rsync akan menggunakan SSH untuk menghubungkan sebagai user untuk <span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">remote-host </span>Setelah terhubung, maka akan memanggil rsync remote host dan kemudian  dua program akan menentukan bagian mana dari file perlu ditransfer  melalui koneksi.</span></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\">&nbsp;</span></span></span> <br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> <span class=\"notranslate\"> rsync juga dapat beroperasi dalam daemon modus, melayani file di protokol rsync asli (menggunakan \"rsync: //\" sintaks).</span></span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\">Mirip dengan rcp dan scp, rsync memerlukan spesifikasi sumber dan tujuan; salah satu dari mereka mungkin jauh, tapi tidak keduanya. Karena fleksibilitas, kecepatan dan scriptability dari rsync telah menjadi utilitas standar Linux, termasuk dalam semua distribusi Linux populer.&nbsp;</span></span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\">Sintaks Umum :&nbsp;</span></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Local:&nbsp; rsync [OPTION...] SRC... [DEST]<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Access via remote shell:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pull: rsync [OPTION...] [USER@]HOST:SRC... [DEST]<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Push: rsync [OPTION...] SRC... [USER@]HOST:DEST<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Access via rsync daemon:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pull: rsync [OPTION...] [USER@]HOST::SRC... [DEST]<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; rsync [OPTION...] rsync://[USER@]HOST[:PORT]/SRC... [DEST]</span></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\"><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Push: rsync [OPTION...] SRC... [USER@]HOST::DEST<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; rsync [OPTION...] SRC... rsync://[USER@]HOST[:PORT]/DEST</span></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\"></span></span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"long_text\" id=\"result_box\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"Usages with just one SRC arg and no DEST arg will list the source files instead of copying. &lt;br&gt;\">Penggunaan </span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"long_text\" id=\"result_box\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"Usages with just one SRC arg and no DEST arg will list the source files instead of copying. &lt;br&gt;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"long_text\" id=\"result_box\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"Usages with just one SRC arg and no DEST arg will list the source files instead of copying. &lt;br&gt;\">dengan</span></span></span></span></span> hanya satu SRC arg dan tidak ada DEST arg akan mendaftar file sumber bukan menyalin. </span></span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\">Contoh S<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">intaks :&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Lo<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">kal&nbsp;</span> </span></span></span></span><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">rsync -a<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">v<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">H</span></span> /copy/ke /di/di<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">sini</span></span>&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></blockquote>Remoter (Open-SSH)<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">rsync -avH -e ssh user@192.168.10.2:/copy/dari /simpan/ke/lokal</blockquote>atau<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">rsync -avH -e ssh /dari/lokal user@192.168.10.3:/simpan/ke/server/ </blockquote><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span class=\"notranslate\">Sumber : <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rsync\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rsync</a>&nbsp;</span></span></span> ', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2015/08/mengenal-rsync-fast-and-extraordinarily.html', 1),
(30, 'Repository Debian 8 \"Jessie\" Indonesia', '2015-08-20', 'Berikut ini merupakan beberapa repository debian 8 yang ada di indonesia,<br /><br />1. DATA UTAMA SURABAYA<br /><br />deb http://kartolo.sby.datautama.net.id/debian/ jessie main contrib non-free<br />deb http://kartolo.sby.datautama.net.id/debian/ jessie-updates main contrib non-free<br />deb http://kartolo.sby.datautama.net.id/debian-security/ jessie/updates main contrib non-free <br /><br /><br />2. KEBO VLSM<br /><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br />deb http://kebo.vlsm.org/debian/ jessie main contrib non-free<br />deb http://kebo.vlsm.org/debian/ jessie-updates main contrib non-free<br />deb http://kebo.vlsm.org/debian-security/ jessie/updates main contrib non-free <br /><br />3. KAMBING-UI<br /><br />deb http://kambing.ui.ac.id/debian/ jessie main contrib non-free<br />deb http://kambing.ui.ac.id/debian/ jessie-updates main contrib non-free<br />deb http://kambing.ui.ac.id/debian-security/ jessie/updates main contrib non-free&amp;nbsp<br /><br />4. UNEJ<br /><br />deb http://mirror.unej.ac.id/debian/ jessie main contrib non-free<br />deb http://mirror.unej.ac.id/debian/ jessie-updates main contrib non-free<br />deb http://mirror.unej.ac.id/debian-security/ jessie/updates main contrib non-free<br /><br />anda dapat memasukan repo tersebut ke \"/etc/apt/source.list\" lalu masukan perintah<br />#apt-get update &amp;&amp; apt-get dist-upgrade ', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2015/08/repository-debian-8-jessie-indonesia.html', 1),
