nda dapat membuka icecast anda dengan membuka ip atau domain anda di port 8000 \"<span class=\"system\">http://192.168.0.100:8000/\"</span> <br /><div class=\"command\"><br /></div>', '', 1),
(60, 'Mengatur Waktu Di Mikrotik Dan Tambahan-nya', '2014-08-27', 'Pastikan Sudah Terkoneksi dengan internet<br /><br />1.klik system -&gt;SNTP Client<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-7z-cjEZXKKs/U_6pB4EupUI/AAAAAAAACXs/RtR0j5U1McU/s1600/system%2Bsntp%2Bclient.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-7z-cjEZXKKs/U_6pB4EupUI/AAAAAAAACXs/RtR0j5U1McU/s1600/system%2Bsntp%2Bclient.png\" height=\"356\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>2.tandai enable mode unicast isikan primary NTP server \"id.pool.ntp.org\" yang kedua isikan \"ntp.nasa.gov\" klik apply ok<br /><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dnPFTpTNFvc/U_6pBaQ9lQI/AAAAAAAACYA/CLsLGQPpqxI/s1600/ntp%2Bclient.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dnPFTpTNFvc/U_6pBaQ9lQI/AAAAAAAACYA/CLsLGQPpqxI/s1600/ntp%2Bclient.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div>3.klik system -&gt; clock<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-T21mcgCHVk0/U_6pBlWuQUI/AAAAAAAACXo/-lq-Y5rlGDY/s1600/system%2Bclock.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-T21mcgCHVk0/U_6pBlWuQUI/AAAAAAAACXo/-lq-Y5rlGDY/s1600/system%2Bclock.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>4.time zone name cari wilayah anda klik apply ok<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3BEiw6xrnG8/U_6o__2tuNI/AAAAAAAACXg/ayBBUZOW16k/s1600/clock.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3BEiw6xrnG8/U_6o__2tuNI/AAAAAAAACXg/ayBBUZOW16k/s1600/clock.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-eyYEl5cOz0M/U_6pAswKxyI/AAAAAAAACXc/elWmz9YxmM0/s1600/clock3.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-eyYEl5cOz0M/U_6pAswKxyI/AAAAAAAACXc/elWmz9YxmM0/s1600/clock3.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div>Menambahkan status CPU Memory dan uptime ini untuk mengetahui resource yang terpakai oleh mikrotik<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-0TlY9z4_Ndc/U_6o_DCbnJI/AAAAAAAACXE/Sn7knEfjWqA/s1600/add%2Bcpu.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-0TlY9z4_Ndc/U_6o_DCbnJI/AAAAAAAACXE/Sn7knEfjWqA/s1600/add%2Bcpu.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-AWT4lBwplTk/U_6o_ExNMdI/AAAAAAAACXA/8H97FpMk5bU/s1600/add%2Bmemory.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-AWT4lBwplTk/U_6o_ExNMdI/AAAAAAAACXA/8H97FpMk5bU/s1600/add%2Bmemory.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-xgnJsZknd6g/U_6o_OU_XfI/AAAAAAAACXI/yZny4BQBtY0/s1600/add%2Buptime.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-xgnJsZknd6g/U_6o_OU_XfI/AAAAAAAACXI/yZny4BQBtY0/s1600/add%2Buptime.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br />', '', 1),
(61, 'Cara Mereset Mikrotik Secara Soft', '2014-08-27', 'Resiko terus-terusan mereset dengan hard reset adalah rusaknya hardware nya maka reset mikrotik harus secara software<br /><br />1.Mereset via WinBox dengan system<br /><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HjYKQBlcoZ4/U_6kpJ3PMbI/AAAAAAAACWw/bIY4gtS5S4A/s1600/reset.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HjYKQBlcoZ4/U_6kpJ3PMbI/AAAAAAAACWw/bIY4gtS5S4A/s1600/reset.png\" height=\"208\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iHccgnWcTkg/U_6kpGgviiI/AAAAAAAACWs/i-oIGa4EPxk/s1600/reset2.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iHccgnWcTkg/U_6kpGgviiI/AAAAAAAACWs/i-oIGa4EPxk/s1600/reset2.png\" height=\"100\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>2.reset Secara CLI dengan perintah<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">system reset-configuration</blockquote>', '', 1);
