(68, 'Mengurangi Dan Menambah Tingkat Kecerahan Monitor Laptop Dengan Terminal CLI', '2014-08-21', '1. Install Aplikasi Nya<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">sudo apt-get install xbacklight  </blockquote>2. Setelah Terintal gunakan perintah:<br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">xbacklight -inc 100</blockquote>Untuk Mengurangi Kecerahan Monitor<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">xbacklight -dec 100</blockquote>Untuk Menambah Kecerahan Monitor ', '', 1),
(69, 'Memformat FlashDisk Melalui Terminal', '2014-08-20', '1.Tancapkan FlashDisk anda Ke PC/Laptop Anda<br />2.Buka Terminal dan masuk sebagai root dengan perintah \"sudo su\"<br />3. Masukan Perintah \"ls /dev/ | grep sd\" Akan Muncul<br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">sda&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;<---ini ...=\"\" anda=\"\" br=\"\" hardisk=\"\">sda1<br />sda2<br />sda3<br />sda4<br />sdb&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;<--ini anda=\"\" br=\"\" flashdisk=\"\"><!----ini--><!-----ini--></--ini></---ini></blockquote><blockquote>sdb1</blockquote>4.Unmount Flashdisk Anda Dengan Perintah \" umount /dev/sdb1\" Apapun yang muncul bukan masalah<br />5.Terahir Format FlashDisk Anda dengan Perintah \"mkfs.vfat <span style=\"color: red;\"></span> /dev/sdb1\"<br />Untuk Menformat Flashdisk Anda Dengan Format FAT ', '', 1),
(70, 'Mengkonfigurasi DNS Server CentOS 6.5 Dengan ISPConfig3', '2014-08-20', '1.anda harus masuk ke isp konfig anda dulu klik DNS,klik add DNS Zone ,Klik Add DNS Zone Manually Isikan sesuai gambar<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-qDLQ2dsYYYQ/U_MgqAY4IlI/AAAAAAAAB2A/ViOX1oNh0ok/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-19%2B15%3A23%3A47.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-qDLQ2dsYYYQ/U_MgqAY4IlI/AAAAAAAAB2A/ViOX1oNh0ok/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-19%2B15%3A23%3A47.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><a name=\'more\'></a><br />2.klik record,buat A ,A ,NS ,NS<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-d8ScBeF5eXQ/U_MgqnGmOHI/AAAAAAAAB2E/DYdumiB4PdY/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-19%2B15%3A24%3A06.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-d8ScBeF5eXQ/U_MgqnGmOHI/AAAAAAAAB2E/DYdumiB4PdY/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-19%2B15%3A24%3A06.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>3.Buat A isikan Hostname dan target sesuai gambar diatas ,Buat NS juga isikan sesuai gambar diatas<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8hlbEMGdurI/U_MgrxYx4AI/AAAAAAAAB2c/xHcyTBdU11U/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-19%2B17%3A01%3A35.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8hlbEMGdurI/U_MgrxYx4AI/AAAAAAAAB2c/xHcyTBdU11U/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-19%2B17%3A01%3A35.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div>4.Coba Anda Dig melalui Terminal dengan Perintah \" dig domain.anda\"<br />jika benar ip anda akan muncul seperti diatas<br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-j38b_pTZatk/U_MgrfAeCPI/AAAAAAAAB2Y/xRhVWh2k8sM/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-19%2B16%3A44%3A03.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-j38b_pTZatk/U_MgrfAeCPI/AAAAAAAAB2Y/xRhVWh2k8sM/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-19%2B16%3A44%3A03.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>5.coba juga menggunakna webrowser jika benar website anda akan muncul ', '', 1),
(71, 'Mengistall NTP-Server DI Debian 7', '2014-08-19', '1. Install aplikasi NTP-Server<br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"># apt-get install ntp ntpdate</blockquote><br />2. Langkah konfigurasinya <br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"># nano /etc/ntp.conf</blockquote><br />Lalu.....cari baris berikut :<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">server 0.debian.pool.ntp.org iburst<br />server 1.debian.pool.ntp.org iburst<br />server 2.debian.pool.ntp.org iburst<br />server 3.debian.pool.ntp.org iburst&nbsp;</blockquote>Kemudian Hapus dan Tambahkan Baris Sepeti dibawah. Hasilnya seperti ini :<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">server 127.127.1.0<br />fudge 127.127.1.0 stratum 1</blockquote><br />Berikutnya cari baris berikut<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">#restrict 192.168.123.0 mask 255.255.255.0 notrust</blockquote><br />Dan ubahlah menjadi seperti ini :<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">restrict 192.168.1.0 mask 255.255.255.0 nomodify notrap </blockquote><br />Lalu restart ntp <br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"># /etc/init.d/ntp restart </blockquote>3. Lalu lakukan pengecekkan dengan cara :<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"># ntpq -p<br />remote refid st t when poll reach delay offset jitter<br />====================================<br />*LOCAL(0) .LOCL. 1 l 14 64 1 0.000 0.000 0.001</blockquote>Jika nilai dari jitter = 0.000, maka konfigurasi masih belum benar, pastikan jitter ini tidak bernilai 0.000<br /><br />Lalu lakukan sinkronisasi dengan localhost, dengan cara :<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"># ntpdate -u 127.0.0.1<br />7 Jun 06:19:35 ntpdate[3951]: adjust time server 127.0.0.1 offset 0.000008 sec </blockquote><br />Jadi client tidak perlu mensetting  waktu secara manual, melainkan hanya meminta kepada si servernya itu.', '', 1),
(72, 'Portal SIM Sekolah edisi Terpadu dengan HTML Sederhana', '2014-08-19', '<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nZgEamaNYxU/U_QVD3YC7uI/AAAAAAAAB24/6xck9e215BU/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-20%2B10%3A24%3A09.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nZgEamaNYxU/U_QVD3YC7uI/AAAAAAAAB24/6xck9e215BU/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-20%2B10%3A24%3A09.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><br />Portal Ini dipersembahkan untuk yang mau mengembangkan sistem informasi sekolah tingkit apapun silahkan download dibawah<br /><br /><a href=\"http://webaji.url.ph/database/uploads/Portal%20Terbuka%20dan%20Terpadu.zip\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">DOWNLOAD</span></span></a><br /><br /><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">cara mengembah kan buat newbie&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><br /><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">1.pahan HTML,CSS,Javascript dll&nbsp;</span></span> </span></span>', '', 1),
(73, 'Mengistall Mysql Server di CentOS 6.5', '2014-08-18', '1.Install Mysql<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">#yum install mysql mysql-server<br /><a name=\'more\'></a></blockquote>2.Nyalakan Service Mysql<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">#service mysqld start</blockquote><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">#chkconfig mysqld start</blockquote>3.Berikan / Set Password Mysql<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">#mysql_secure_installation </blockquote><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">root@server1:~# mysql_secure_installation <br /><br />NOTE: RUNNING ALL PARTS OF THIS SCRIPT IS RECOMMENDED FOR ALL MySQL<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SERVERS IN PRODUCTION USE!&nbsp; PLEASE READ EACH STEP CAREFULLY!<br /><br />In order to log into MySQL to secure it, we\'ll need the current<br />password for the root user.&nbsp; If you\'ve just installed MySQL, and<br />you haven\'t set the root password yet, the password will be blank,<br />so you should just press enter here.<br />Enter current password for root (enter for none):&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;<--biarkan kosong=\"\" span=\"\"><br />OK, successfully used password, moving on...<br />Setting the root password ensures that nobody can log into the MySQL<br />root user without the proper authorisation.<br />You already have a root password set, so you can safely answer \'n\'.<br />Change the root password? [Y/n]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;<-- enter=\"\" span=\"\"><br />New password:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;<--password span=\"\"><br />Re-enter new password:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\">&nbsp; &lt;<--ulangi span=\"\"><br />Password updated successfully!<br />Reloading privilege tables..<br />&nbsp;... Success!<br />By default, a MySQL installation has an anonymous user, allowing anyone<br />to log into MySQL without having to have a user account created for<br />them.&nbsp; This is intended only for testing, and to make the installation<br />go a bit smoother.&nbsp; You should remove them before moving into a<br />production environment.<br />Remove anonymous users? [Y/n]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"> &lt;<--enter span=\"\"><br />&nbsp;... Success!<br />Normally, root should only be allowed to connect from \'localhost\'.&nbsp; This<br />ensures that someone cannot guess at the root password from the network.<br />Disallow root login remotely? [Y/n] n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"> &lt;<--enter span=\"\"><br />&nbsp;... skipping.<br />By default, MySQL comes with a database named \'test\' that anyone can<br />access.&nbsp; This is also intended only for testing, and should be removed<br />before moving into a production environment.<br />Remove test database and access to it? [Y/n]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"> &lt;<--enter span=\"\"><br />&nbsp;- Dropping test database...<br />&nbsp;... Success!<br />&nbsp;- Removing privileges on test database...<br />&nbsp;... Success!<br />Reloading the privilege tables will ensure that all changes made so far<br />will take effect immediately.<br />Reload privilege tables now? [Y/n]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"> &lt;<--enter span=\"\"><br />&nbsp;... Success!<br />Cleaning up...<br />All done!&nbsp; If you\'ve completed all of the above steps, your MySQL<br />installation should now be secure.<br />Thanks for using MySQL!<!----enter--><!----enter--></--enter></span><!----enter--><!----enter--></--enter></span><!----enter--><!----enter--></--enter></span><!----enter--><!----enter--></--enter></span><!----ulangi--><!----ulangi--></--ulangi></span><!----password--><!----password--></--password></span><!------><!------></--></span><!----biarkan--><!----biarkan--></--biarkan></span></span></blockquote>', '', 1),
(74, 'Mengistall WebServer di CentOS 6.5', '2014-08-18', '1.Install httpd<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">#yum install httpd <br /><a name=\'more\'></a></blockquote>Nyalakan service httpd <br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"># service httpd start </blockquote><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"># chkconfig httpd on </blockquote>2.Buka Webrowser anda dan coba akses IP server anda<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-G2mB0z0wapY/U_H2w1Lj9LI/AAAAAAAAB1s/jRw-ju3BFFQ/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-18%2B17%3A04%3A55.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-G2mB0z0wapY/U_H2w1Lj9LI/AAAAAAAAB1s/jRw-ju3BFFQ/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-18%2B17%3A04%3A55.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>Buka juga <a href=\"http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/08/hal-hal-yang-harus-dilakukan-setelah.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hal-hal yang harus dilakukan setelah install Centos</a>', '', 1);
