(75, 'SElinux CentOS', '2014-08-16', '<span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\">Security <span class=\"hps\">Enhanced</span> <span class=\"hps\">Linux</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">(</span>SELinux) <span class=\"hps\">adalah</span> <span class=\"hps\">keamanan</span> <span class=\"hps\">kernel</span> <span class=\"hps\">modul</span> <span class=\"hps\">Linux</span> <span class=\"hps\">yang menyediakan</span> <span class=\"hps\">mekanisme</span> <span class=\"hps\">untuk</span> <span class=\"hps\">mendukung</span> <span class=\"hps\">kebijakan keamanan</span> <span class=\"hps\">kontrol akses</span>, <span class=\"hps\">termasuk</span> <span class=\"hps\">Amerika</span> <span class=\"hps\">Serikat Departemen Pertahanan</span> <span class=\"hps\">gaya</span> <span class=\"hps\">kontrol</span> <span class=\"hps\">akses mandatory</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">(</span>MAC). </span><br /><a name=\'more\'></a><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><br /><span class=\"hps\">SELinux</span> <span class=\"hps\">adalah</span> <span class=\"hps\">set modifikasi</span> <span class=\"hps\">kernel</span> <span class=\"hps\">dan alat</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">user-</span>space <span class=\"hps\">yang</span> <span class=\"hps\">dapat ditambahkan ke</span> <span class=\"hps\">berbagai distribusi</span> <span class=\"hps\">Linux.</span> <span class=\"hps\">Arsitekturnya</span> <span class=\"hps\">berusaha untuk</span> <span class=\"hps\">memisahkan</span> <span class=\"hps\">penegakan keputusan</span> <span class=\"hps\">keamanan dari</span> <span class=\"hps\">kebijakan keamanan</span> <span class=\"hps\">sendiri</span> <span class=\"hps\">dan arus</span> <span class=\"hps\">volume</span> <span class=\"hps\">software</span> <span class=\"hps\">diisi dengan</span> <span class=\"hps\">penegakan</span> <span class=\"hps\">kebijakan keamanan</span>.</span><br /><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps atn\"></span><span class=\"hps atn\"></span> <span class=\"hps\">Konsep</span> <span class=\"hps\">utama yang mendasari</span> <span class=\"hps\">SELinux</span> <span class=\"hps\">dapat ditelusuri ke</span> <span class=\"hps\">beberapa proyek</span> <span class=\"hps\">sebelumnya oleh</span> <span class=\"hps\">National Security</span> <span class=\"hps\">Amerika</span> <span class=\"hps\">Serikat</span> <span class=\"hps\">Agency.</span></span> <br /><br />Referansi : <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Security-Enhanced_Linux\" target=\"_blank\">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Security-Enhanced_Linux </a><br /><br />Sepaham Saya, SELinux ini jika tetap enable atau aktif maka konfigurasi ataupun instalasi yang dilakukan pada server akan hilang ketika server dimatikan atau di reboot', '', 1),
(76, 'Hal-Hal Yang Harus Dilakukan Setelah Install CentOS Server', '2014-08-16', '1. Setting IP Static (jika belum)<br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><br /><a name=\'more\'></a># system-config-network</blockquote>Dengan perintah diatas anda dapat menyeting ip ,gateway dan dns<br /><br />2.Matikan Firewall-tui <br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"># system-config-firewall-tui</blockquote>Anda Harus mendisable firewall default nya<br />contoh:<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">[root@server1&nbsp;~]#&nbsp;iptables&nbsp;-L</blockquote><blockquote>Chain&nbsp;INPUT&nbsp;(policy&nbsp;ACCEPT)<br />target&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;prot&nbsp;opt&nbsp;source&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;destination<br /><br />Chain&nbsp;FORWARD&nbsp;(policy&nbsp;ACCEPT)<br />target&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;prot&nbsp;opt&nbsp;source&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;destination<br /><br />Chain&nbsp;OUTPUT&nbsp;(policy&nbsp;ACCEPT)<br />target&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;prot&nbsp;opt&nbsp;source&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;destination</blockquote><br />3. Matikan SELinux<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">#vi /etc/selinux/config</blockquote>&nbsp;script nya :<br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><pre># This file controls the state of SELinux on the system.<br /># SELINUX= can take one of these three values:<br />#     enforcing - SELinux security policy is enforced.<br />#     permissive - SELinux prints warnings instead of enforcing.<br />#     disabled - No SELinux policy is loaded.<br />SELINUX=disabled                                             &lt;<-----menjadi -=\"\" are=\"\" disable=\"\" level=\"\" mls=\"\" multi=\"\" of=\"\" one=\"\" processes=\"\" protected=\"\" protection.=\"\" security=\"\" selinuxtype=\"targeted&lt;/pre\" take=\"\" targeted=\"\" these=\"\" two=\"\" values:=\"\"><!-------menjadi--><!-------menjadi--></-----menjadi></pre></blockquote></blockquote>&nbsp;4.Samakan Hostname<br />Cek dengan perintah seperti dibawah <br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">root@server1 ~ # hostname</blockquote><blockquote>server1.com<br />root@server1 ~ # hostname -f<br />server1.com.com</blockquote>jika belum sama seperti di atas coba<br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\">#vi /etc/hosts</blockquote><pre>127.0.0.1   localhost localhost.localdomain localhost4 localhost4.localdomain4<br />192.168.12.50   server1.com     server1                                         &lt;<---tambahkan ::1=\"\" localhost.localdomain=\"\" localhost6.localdomain6=\"\" localhost6=\"\" localhost=\"\" pre=\"\"><br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><br />#Reboot</blockquote><br />&nbsp;5.Update system<br /><br /><blockquote class=\"tr_bq\"><br />#yum update</blockquote><br />&nbsp;<!-----tambahkan--><!-----tambahkan--></---tambahkan></pre>', '', 1),
(77, 'KVM Server Install Dan Kendalikan Dengan Virt-manager Client Linux mint', '2014-08-15', '<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div>1.Untuk Mengistall KVM Dulu di server Anda <a href=\"http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/08/virtualisasi-dengan-kvm-di-debian-7.html\" target=\"_blank\">Klik disini</a><br /><br />2.Setelah Anda Install KVM nya Install Virt-manager Di client anda (Linux mint)<br />dengan Perintah \" apt-get install virt-manager\"<br /><a name=\'more\'></a><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kaHBwhbCIMU/U-3hyGEBwlI/AAAAAAAABsQ/HGL5zjkY91c/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A27%3A40.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kaHBwhbCIMU/U-3hyGEBwlI/AAAAAAAABsQ/HGL5zjkY91c/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A27%3A40.png\" height=\"73\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>3.Buka Virt-manager anda dengan perintah \" virt-manager \"<br />Akan ada error seperti dibawah close saja<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nnt0J9evWCc/U-3hyTX4IpI/AAAAAAAABsY/V2uAm3RxGd4/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A28%3A08.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nnt0J9evWCc/U-3hyTX4IpI/AAAAAAAABsY/V2uAm3RxGd4/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A28%3A08.png\" height=\"222\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>4.Setelah Terbuka Delete localhost(QEMU) anda<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WKIgHzG7ehg/U-3hzKU7-lI/AAAAAAAABsk/o7X49DN6QQ0/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A28%3A48.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WKIgHzG7ehg/U-3hzKU7-lI/AAAAAAAABsk/o7X49DN6QQ0/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A28%3A48.png\" height=\"223\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>5.Buat koneksi baru ke server anda dengan memilih add connection<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-TYOJwoEVyrY/U-3hzTbPe6I/AAAAAAAABss/Avnfx1DNrMU/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A29%3A48.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-TYOJwoEVyrY/U-3hzTbPe6I/AAAAAAAABss/Avnfx1DNrMU/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A29%3A48.png\" height=\"222\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>6.isikan seperti gambar dibawah dan sesuikan denga ip server anda klik connect<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-A7iqRVcja5c/U-3h0NR5c3I/AAAAAAAABs4/N_1Uj73u8nU/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A30%3A16.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-A7iqRVcja5c/U-3h0NR5c3I/AAAAAAAABs4/N_1Uj73u8nU/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A30%3A16.png\" height=\"223\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>7.setelah anda terkoneksi buat VM(virtual machine ) baru dengan meng-klik Create a new virtual machine<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-g39e-eHzIvY/U-3h0Ub-uWI/AAAAAAAABs8/e2wcvHBpNMc/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A30%3A51.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-g39e-eHzIvY/U-3h0Ub-uWI/AAAAAAAABs8/e2wcvHBpNMc/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A30%3A51.png\" height=\"223\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>8.ikuti langkah-langkah pada gambar dibawah <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-gwgo_rEoE70/U-3h0n2T7uI/AAAAAAAABtA/S7UPxyYYMCY/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A30%3A57.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-gwgo_rEoE70/U-3h0n2T7uI/AAAAAAAABtA/S7UPxyYYMCY/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A30%3A57.png\" height=\"223\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>9. saya memilih Network Installasion Karena pasti mendapatkan versi terbaru<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lTelIDxkHOY/U-3h1TL5qII/AAAAAAAABtU/4sRiZ7pxTUY/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A31%3A05.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lTelIDxkHOY/U-3h1TL5qII/AAAAAAAABtU/4sRiZ7pxTUY/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A31%3A05.png\" height=\"223\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>10.masukan link <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-YJD9Y_Gmi6o/U-3h1hZ4UvI/AAAAAAAABtY/dklxQ1Yt1P4/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A31%3A23.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-YJD9Y_Gmi6o/U-3h1hZ4UvI/AAAAAAAABtY/dklxQ1Yt1P4/s1600/Screenshot%2Bfrom%2B2014-08-15%2B15%3A31%3A23.png\" height=\"223\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>beberapa link yang layak anda coba :<br /><ul><li><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\">link location 32bit debian : http://ftp.riken.jp/Linux/debian/debian/dists/wheezy/main/installer-i386/</span></span><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\">&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\">link location 64bit debian : http://ftp.riken.jp/Linux/debian/debian/dists/wheezy/main/installer-amd64/</span></span><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\">link location 32bit CentOS : http://mirror.facebook.net/centos/6.5/os/i386/</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\">link location 64bit CentOS</span></span></span></span></span></span> :http://mirror.facebook.net/centos/6.5/os/x86_64/</span></span><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"></span></span></span></span></li><li><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><br /></span></span></span></span></li></ul><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\">11.klik forward , masukan dulu berapa ram yang anda inginkan dan jumlah prosesor nya</span></span></span></span><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QXZnbL3XZEU/U-3h17S5yDI/AAAAAAAABtc/Lvzbuha2xSY/s1600/Screenshot