(78, 'Mengistall CentOS 6.5', '2014-08-15', '1.Boot Centos ke server anda, pilih install tekan enter seperti ganbar dibawah<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tR2EX8t7788/U-9sSkJlKfI/AAAAAAAABzQ/SGdARlRZOHs/s1600/1.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tR2EX8t7788/U-9sSkJlKfI/AAAAAAAABzQ/SGdARlRZOHs/s1600/1.png\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>2.muncul seperti dibawah tekan tap untuk menentukan pilihan pilih skip tekan<br /><a name=\'more\'></a>enter<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-g8aB6DdA9hY/U-9soGAef8I/AAAAAAAAB0U/MiNx4Nwrw3s/s1600/2.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-g8aB6DdA9hY/U-9soGAef8I/AAAAAAAAB0U/MiNx4Nwrw3s/s1600/2.png\" height=\"222\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>3.muncul seperti gambar dibawah klik next<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fEh2YIcw-co/U-9srSKb_RI/AAAAAAAAB0c/j-Oky4mjMxQ/s1600/3.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fEh2YIcw-co/U-9srSKb_RI/AAAAAAAAB0c/j-Oky4mjMxQ/s1600/3.png\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>4.pilih bahasa klik next<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yg8k3yMyqKY/U-9sv3efvYI/AAAAAAAAB0k/Xh57cj3mMDQ/s1600/4.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yg8k3yMyqKY/U-9sv3efvYI/AAAAAAAAB0k/Xh57cj3mMDQ/s1600/4.png\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>5.pilih type keybord us amerika klik next<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspo