(97, 'Mengubah Sedikit warna tulisan dalam grub', '2014-04-25', '1.ketika booting di grub anda muncul silahkan tekan \"c\"<br />2.muncul \"grup&gt;\"<br />3.masukan perintah \"set\"<br />secara standart muncul:<br /><style type=\"text/css\">P { margin-bottom: 0.08in; }</style>   <br /><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">?=o</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">color_highlight=black/white</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">color_normal=white/black</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">default=0</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">feature_timeout_style=y</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">gfxmode=auto</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">have_grubenv=true</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">lang=en_US</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">linux_gfx_mode=keep</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">locale_dir=(hd0,msdos1)/boot/grub/locale</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">menu_color_highlight=white/black</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">menu_color_normal=black/white</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">normal=white/dark</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">pager=</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">prefix=(hd0,msdos1)/boot/grub</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">root=hd0,msdos1</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">timeout_style=menu</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br /></div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">untuk menganti sedikit tulisan silahkan masukan perintah pada pilihan berikut :<br /><br /><a name=\'more\'></a>&nbsp;</div><ul><li><div class=\"line891\"><tt class=\"backtick\">set&nbsp;color_normal=color1/color2</tt> <span class=\"anchor\" id=\"line-190\"></span></div></li><li><div class=\"line891\"><tt class=\"backtick\">set&nbsp;color_highlight=color1/color2</tt> <span class=\"anchor\" id=\"line-191\"></span></div></li><li><div class=\"line891\"><tt class=\"backtick\">set&nbsp;menu_color=color1/color2</tt></div><div class=\"line891\"></div></li></ul><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">warna-warna yang tersedia :<br /><img alt=\"g2_splash_color-edit.png\" class=\"attachment\" height=\"355\" src=\"https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Grub2/Displays?action=AttachFile&amp;do=get&amp;target=g2_splash_color-edit.png\" title=\"g2_splash_color-edit.png\" width=\"640\" /></div><br />sumber informasi : <a href=\"https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Grub2/Displays\">https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Grub2/Displays</a>', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/04/mengubah-sedikit-warna-tulisan-dalam.html', 1),
