(112, 'Mengistall Proftpd di Ubuntu 12.04', '2014-04-10', '<b>Protokol pengiriman berkas</b> (<a href=\"http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bahasa_Inggris\" title=\"Bahasa Inggris\">bahasa Inggris</a>: <span lang=\"en\"><i>File Transfer Protocol</i></span>) adalah sebuah <a href=\"http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protokol_Internet\" title=\"Protokol Internet\">protokol Internet</a> yang berjalan di dalam <a href=\"http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lapisan_aplikasi\" title=\"Lapisan aplikasi\">lapisan aplikasi</a> yang merupakan standar untuk pengiriman <a href=\"http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Berkas_komputer\" title=\"Berkas komputer\">berkas</a> (<i>file</i>) <a href=\"http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Komputer\" title=\"Komputer\">komputer</a> antar mesin-mesin dalam sebuah <a href=\"http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antarjaringan\" title=\"Antarjaringan\">Antarjaringan</a>.(sumber : <a href=\"http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protokol_Transfer_Berkas\">http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protokol_Transfer_Berkas</a>)<br /><br /><br /><br />Langkah-langkah mengistall proftpd:<br />1.buka terminal masuk sebagai root dengan perintah \"sudo su\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-RnvhK7Z0osU/U0ZH6PkihqI/AAAAAAAABOo/EN7lZLYxlZk/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:21:42.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-RnvhK7Z0osU/U0ZH6PkihqI/AAAAAAAABOo/EN7lZLYxlZk/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:21:42.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>2.install aplikasi proftpd dengan perintah \"apt-get install proftpd\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-QBLRNOVdCIM/U0ZH7NCH-eI/AAAAAAAABOw/PcBVucbWKDU/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:22:02.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-QBLRNOVdCIM/U0ZH7NCH-eI/AAAAAAAABOw/PcBVucbWKDU/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:22:02.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>3.muncul pilihan pilih standalone dengan tekan tap lalu tekan entar<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-52o26j91D3A/U0ZH7zfuQqI/AAAAAAAABO0/RynaYufe_mo/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:22:31.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-52o26j91D3A/U0ZH7zfuQqI/AAAAAAAABO0/RynaYufe_mo/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:22:31.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9X7qOIr_8gk/U0ZH-KysM6I/AAAAAAAABPA/y7HLEGQmvM8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:22:35.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9X7qOIr_8gk/U0ZH-KysM6I/AAAAAAAABPA/y7HLEGQmvM8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:22:35.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>4.edit file proftpd.conf dengan perintah \"vi /etc/proftpd/proftpd.conf\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nAMr0FzxR88/U0ZIA1o6KUI/AAAAAAAABPI/6oVMO51aIao/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:23:18.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nAMr0FzxR88/U0ZIA1o6KUI/AAAAAAAABPI/6oVMO51aIao/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:23:18.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>5.pada baris ke 11 ganti on pada UseIPv6 menjadi off seperti dua gambar dibawah<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-8RBRo1VZW0c/U0ZIBF6JX6I/AAAAAAAABPM/BtqVcI36caU/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:23:27.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-8RBRo1VZW0c/U0ZIBF6JX6I/AAAAAAAABPM/BtqVcI36caU/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:23:27.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>6.pada baris ke 15 ganti server name seperti gambar:<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-sDbxvxQThpQ/U0ZIB_rlDsI/AAAAAAAABPU/wYi-9_aHQlE/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:24:04.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-sDbxvxQThpQ/U0ZIB_rlDsI/AAAAAAAABPU/wYi-9_aHQlE/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:24:04.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>7.cari # DefaultRoot ~ seperti gambar dibawah lalu hilangkan tanda pagarnya <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--nQ3bOwIiFo/U0ZIFtP32EI/AAAAAAAABPg/a2SQcHMPjzc/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:24:12.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--nQ3bOwIiFo/U0ZIFtP32EI/AAAAAAAABPg/a2SQcHMPjzc/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:24:12.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>8.tekan esc lalu tekan shift+: tekan w dan q tekan enter<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-2E5z2ZyrJq8/U0ZIGuWWmMI/AAAAAAAABPs/-cdkMRuvtxo/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:24:15.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-2E5z2ZyrJq8/U0ZIGuWWmMI/AAAAAAAABPs/-cdkMRuvtxo/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:24:15.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-yyC3mpsaeH8/U0ZIGPe54DI/AAAAAAAABPk/3znQfeVULy4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:24:27.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-yyC3mpsaeH8/U0ZIGPe54DI/AAAAAAAABPk/3znQfeVULy4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:24:27.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div>9.restart proftpd dengan perintah di terminal \"service proftpd restart\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Xb_Y13bhgm8/U0ZIMCTYw6I/AAAAAAAABQA/Dvz0UZ1dRxA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:25:59.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Xb_Y13bhgm8/U0ZIMCTYw6I/AAAAAAAABQA/Dvz0UZ1dRxA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:25:59.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4Whilf_hZbA/U0ZIMxXhqgI/AAAAAAAABQI/pEUdkMexUgY/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:26:04.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-4Whilf_hZbA/U0ZIMxXhqgI/AAAAAAAABQI/pEUdkMexUgY/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:26:04.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>10.coba di browser dengan alamat ftp://localhost masukan username dan password <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Hjc5UuQCPP0/U0ZIM2mPACI/AAAAAAAABQE/PM2tJkNMcMA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:26:44.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Hjc5UuQCPP0/U0ZIM2mPACI/AAAAAAAABQE/PM2tJkNMcMA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:26:44.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-lz-N_pcOZkU/U0ZINixXkuI/AAAAAAAABQU/EEnosyodIrM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:26:48.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-lz-N_pcOZkU/U0ZINixXkuI/AAAAAAAABQU/EEnosyodIrM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:26:48.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br />', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/04/mengistall-proftpd-di-ubuntu-1204.html', 1),
(113, 'Mengubah background GNU Group Loader', '2014-04-10', '1.siapkan gambar untu mengantinya dengan ukuran kurang lebih 500 x 370px dengan format .png<br />atau anda dapat download gambar ini <a href=\"http://webaji.url.ph/database/uploads/desktop-grub.png\" target=\"_blank\">desktop-grub.png </a><br /><br />2.masuk ke terminal masuk sebagai root dengan perintah \"sudo su\"<br />3.backup gambar asli dengan perintah \"cp /usr/share/images/desktop-base/desktop-grub.png /home/(nama)/Picture\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-U6u7bUl5k_w/U0ZCxrJkOmI/AAAAAAAABNw/yCrr3o7kjb8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:02:29.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-U6u7bUl5k_w/U0ZCxrJkOmI/AAAAAAAABNw/yCrr3o7kjb8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:02:29.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>4.ubah nama gambar yang anda ingin jadikan background grub tadi dengan nama \"desktop-grub.png\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vNX1pWxq6kk/U0ZCwhzmX9I/AAAAAAAABNY/_zy7ynhQbww/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:02:42.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vNX1pWxq6kk/U0ZCwhzmX9I/AAAAAAAABNY/_zy7ynhQbww/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:02:42.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-wwph1nyvoDY/U0ZCx__HhLI/AAAAAAAABNo/UrOovzWOPj8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:04:26.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-wwph1nyvoDY/U0ZCx__HhLI/AAAAAAAABNo/UrOovzWOPj8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:04:26.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>5.pindahkan file gambar anda tadi ke /usr/share/images/desktop-base/ dengan perintah \"cp desktop-grup.png /usr/share/images/desktop-base/\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-D0_MMSyhTGI/U0ZCzXImOaI/AAAAAAAABN4/bTJUvHm3KXc/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:04:57.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-D0_MMSyhTGI/U0ZCzXImOaI/AAAAAAAABN4/bTJUvHm3KXc/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:04:57.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>6.coba reboot untuk memeriksa jika tidak ada perubahan atau gambar hilang mungkin ada kesalahan <br /><br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><br /><br /><br />', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/04/mengubah-background-gnu-group-loader.html', 1),
(114, 'Mengubah Jendal cinnamon menjadi wobbly atay seperti agar-agar goyang', '2014-04-10', '1.pastikan tipe desktop cinnamon<br />2.download ekstensi wobbly di <a href=\"http://cinnamon-spices.linuxmint.com/extensions/view/24\">http://cinnamon-spices.linuxmint.com/extensions/view/24</a><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-eJupBBkXdcE/U0Y88IygTWI/AAAAAAAABMg/n3av4DFIN1o/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:36:44.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-eJupBBkXdcE/U0Y88IygTWI/AAAAAAAABMg/n3av4DFIN1o/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:36:44.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;3.setelah uduh pindah kan file .zip tadi ke \"/home/(nama user)/.local/share/cinnamon/extensions\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-kLjiLwxZReo/U0Y877yUIXI/AAAAAAAABMY/CoC0apjVCUk/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:37:45.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-kLjiLwxZReo/U0Y877yUIXI/AAAAAAAABMY/CoC0apjVCUk/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:37:45.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;4.exstrak file yang anda download ke sana<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8ccZNdLdIMg/U0Y88Mvl9YI/AAAAAAAABMc/meP_SaWQV2Y/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:38:07.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8ccZNdLdIMg/U0Y88Mvl9YI/AAAAAAAABMc/meP_SaWQV2Y/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:38:07.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-oMP83coN2aQ/U0Y88wh2RmI/AAAAAAAABM0/ep2eicxWmWs/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:38:15.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-oMP83coN2aQ/U0Y88wh2RmI/AAAAAAAABM0/ep2eicxWmWs/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:38:15.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DB3-7urR2e4/U0Y887pXDEI/AAAAAAAABMw/ktLjdJr5SPg/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:38:35.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DB3-7urR2e4/U0Y887pXDEI/AAAAAAAABMw/ktLjdJr5SPg/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:38:35.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;5.setelah anda ekstrak restart cinnamon anda dengan klik kanan pada panel seperti gambar klik troubleshoot klik restrat atau melalui terminal dengan perintah \"cinnamon --replace\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-eCqYtjHTTWk/U0Y89JMqW-I/AAAAAAAABM4/9C8IKVwF8FE/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:38:45.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-eCqYtjHTTWk/U0Y89JMqW-I/AAAAAAAABM4/9C8IKVwF8FE/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:38:45.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;6.kemudian aktifkan cinnamon dengan masuk system setting =&gt; exstensions =&gt; wobbly windows add to cinnamon seperti gambar jadilah kayak ager-ager<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-LbVdsnwZyqI/U0Y8-Q4NGEI/AAAAAAAABNI/NDn4utBZlbs/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:39:43.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-LbVdsnwZyqI/U0Y8-Q4NGEI/AAAAAAAABNI/NDn4utBZlbs/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+13:39:43.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><span style=\"font-size: large;\">ATAU</span><br /><br />1.anda dapat mengantinya dengan lebih mudah yaitu denga cara masuk ke system setting =&gt; exstensions =&gt; klik get more online =&gt; klik refresh list<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xDFK2TTicuA/U0ZEaplbJlI/AAAAAAAABOQ/ozPl54J-nxU/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:10:20.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xDFK2TTicuA/U0ZEaplbJlI/AAAAAAAABOQ/ozPl54J-nxU/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:10:20.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;2.akan muncul banyak extensi silahkan pilih wobbly windows centang dan klik install or update selected<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xEDRmyUsm6c/U0ZEZ5SfrSI/AAAAAAAABOM/zEYaaCzZGMM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:10:56.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xEDRmyUsm6c/U0ZEZ5SfrSI/AAAAAAAABOM/zEYaaCzZGMM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:10:56.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;3. setelah terinstall kembali masuk ke installed pilih wobbly tadi klik lalu klik add to cinnamon<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-69r60kAB8W4/U0ZEbvsSH3I/AAAAAAAABOc/CiYQSTcQ20Y/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:11:11.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-69r60kAB8W4/U0ZEbvsSH3I/AAAAAAAABOc/CiYQSTcQ20Y/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+14:11:11.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp; ', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/04/mengubah-jendal-cinnamon-menjadi-wobbly.html', 1);
