(115, 'Install CMS Lokomedia di Ubuntu 12.04', '2014-04-09', '<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">CMS LOKOMEDIA adalah salah satu CMS (Content System Management) buatan  anak negeri yang tak kalah menarik seperti CMS yang lainnya. Kalian  dapat menggunakan untuk web Intansi, sekolah maupun web pribadi, karena  CMS ini cocok digunakan untuk beberapa keperluan yang mana tersedia  beberapa modul yang siap pakai.&nbsp;</span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Website Resmi CMS lokomedia : <a href=\"http://bukulokomedia.com/\">http://bukulokomedia.com/</a> </span></span><br /><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Download CMS Lokomedia : </span></span><a href=\"http://bukulokomedia.com/lokomedia-1.6.1.zip\" target=\"_blank\"><b>http://bukulokomedia.com/lokomedia-1.6.1.zip</b></a><br /><br /><br />Langkah-Langkah Mengistall CMS Lokomedia :<br />1. pastikan anda sudah download cms nya , masuk ke terminal masuk sebagai root dengan perintah \"sudo su\" pindah kan file cms yang anda download tadi dengan perintah \"mv lokomedia-1.6.1.zip /var/www/\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-CM2xqCb0hRU/U0TbmtW-TXI/AAAAAAAABJE/EYHtkJb4x8I/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:02:40.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-CM2xqCb0hRU/U0TbmtW-TXI/AAAAAAAABJE/EYHtkJb4x8I/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:02:40.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;2. silahkan anda pindah folder ke /var/www dengan perintah \"cd /var/www\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2uxA_zIyG5U/U0Tbb-Rvg4I/AAAAAAAABI8/Ybq2dxZ55Vs/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:03:55.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2uxA_zIyG5U/U0Tbb-Rvg4I/AAAAAAAABI8/Ybq2dxZ55Vs/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:03:55.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;3.ekstrak file yang anda download dengan perintah \"unzip lokomedia-1.6.1.zip\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AowmR-9G6Is/U0TflNw7TVI/AAAAAAAABL0/dJdIbU43mf8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:04:08.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AowmR-9G6Is/U0TflNw7TVI/AAAAAAAABL0/dJdIbU43mf8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:04:08.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>&nbsp;4.berikan hak akses folder lokomedia dengan perintah \"chown -R www-data:www-data lokomedia\" dan juga dengan perintah \"chmod 755 lokomedia/\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xZFF34h9lmw/U0TcPiKLRuI/AAAAAAAABJM/ziLVY5KlthM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:04:32.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xZFF34h9lmw/U0TcPiKLRuI/AAAAAAAABJM/ziLVY5KlthM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:04:32.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-J9UEJX0T6uU/U0TfdEXieUI/AAAAAAAABLk/_DH_h5q20h0/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:13:13.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-J9UEJX0T6uU/U0TfdEXieUI/AAAAAAAABLk/_DH_h5q20h0/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:13:13.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>5.aktifkan mode rewrite dengan perintah \"a2emod rewrite\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wL4bw4MKZTM/U0TdqtfgB3I/AAAAAAAABJU/ak82hRfvrzQ/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:05:32.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wL4bw4MKZTM/U0TdqtfgB3I/AAAAAAAABJU/ak82hRfvrzQ/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:05:32.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>6.restart apache anda dengan perintah \"service apache2 restart\" atau dengan perintah \"/etc/init.d/apache2 restart\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_0uBrf2DOO4/U0Td-IuyldI/AAAAAAAABJc/YcUnCd1H4ZI/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:05:57.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_0uBrf2DOO4/U0Td-IuyldI/AAAAAAAABJc/YcUnCd1H4ZI/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:05:57.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-msHxqVvoX3s/U0Tehl9eEkI/AAAAAAAABJ0/GBS6Z_rd2MQ/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:06:03.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-msHxqVvoX3s/U0Tehl9eEkI/AAAAAAAABJ0/GBS6Z_rd2MQ/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:06:03.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>7. edit file apache default agar dapat di rewrite dengan perintah \"gedit /etc/apache2/sites-enabled/000-default\" sesuai gambar<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4gJAVfGtqH0/U0TeOaNB7qI/AAAAAAAABJk/rQGy8Qija3o/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:06:35.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4gJAVfGtqH0/U0TeOaNB7qI/AAAAAAAABJk/rQGy8Qija3o/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:06:35.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>8.akan muncul jendela aplikasi gedit silahkan edit sesuai gambar yaitu dari AllowOverride None menjadi AllowOverride All seperti gambar dibawah:<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WqgauYaY8bk/U0TeX-svOaI/AAAAAAAABJs/fS32xsdsFtA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:07:40.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WqgauYaY8bk/U0TeX-svOaI/AAAAAAAABJs/fS32xsdsFtA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:07:40.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-HAMubZTOGuY/U0TemQwifWI/AAAAAAAABJ8/a_xXK6b_w0M/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:07:58.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-HAMubZTOGuY/U0TemQwifWI/AAAAAAAABJ8/a_xXK6b_w0M/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:07:58.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>9.setelah diedit restart apache anda lagi dengan perintah \"service apache2 restart\"<br />10.buka browser dengan memasukan alamat \"localhost/phpmyadmin\" login<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-DvfFYd3cEkI/U0TephZhgTI/AAAAAAAABKI/owSo1LzuLtI/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:09:08.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-DvfFYd3cEkI/U0TephZhgTI/AAAAAAAABKI/owSo1LzuLtI/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:09:08.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>11.klik database<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tT5Teh3eZq4/U0Tepp3wRwI/AAAAAAAABKE/ViPu-XkbVso/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:09:15.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tT5Teh3eZq4/U0Tepp3wRwI/AAAAAAAABKE/ViPu-XkbVso/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:09:15.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>12.masukan nama database dan klik create atau ciptakan<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-02aW3J5SyKI/U0Ter6aBy0I/AAAAAAAABKU/dQMZBwF-YxY/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:09:25.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-02aW3J5SyKI/U0Ter6aBy0I/AAAAAAAABKU/dQMZBwF-YxY/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:09:25.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>13.klik nama database<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-D2n6EKWXE3g/U0Teumgd5bI/AAAAAAAABKc/-owcN_74ScM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:07.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-D2n6EKWXE3g/U0Teumgd5bI/AAAAAAAABKc/-owcN_74ScM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:07.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>14.klik import<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DBEZAH8LVMQ/U0TexBwHZiI/AAAAAAAABKk/8IyzAVQU2ag/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:13.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DBEZAH8LVMQ/U0TexBwHZiI/AAAAAAAABKk/8IyzAVQU2ag/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:13.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>15.klik choose file<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GkAPLtaMoac/U0TexuauYrI/AAAAAAAABKs/JXQZsrS-waw/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:18.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GkAPLtaMoac/U0TexuauYrI/AAAAAAAABKs/JXQZsrS-waw/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:18.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>16 cari sql lokomedian yaitu ada di /var/www/ dengan nama dblokomedia.sql klik go<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ZBdXhDxJqjM/U0Te0X3DF7I/AAAAAAAABK0/eZD8z2M_qwA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:39.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ZBdXhDxJqjM/U0Te0X3DF7I/AAAAAAAABK0/eZD8z2M_qwA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:39.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NmAWy09RvFA/U0Te1sJ6XyI/AAAAAAAABK8/dOMLgK_24yM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:46.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NmAWy09RvFA/U0Te1sJ6XyI/AAAAAAAABK8/dOMLgK_24yM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:10:46.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-P9bWd19V1sI/U0Te-D5Kb5I/AAAAAAAABLE/MKB7hrxtyC4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:11:04.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-P9bWd19V1sI/U0Te-D5Kb5I/AAAAAAAABLE/MKB7hrxtyC4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:11:04.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>17. kembali ke terminal dan edit file koneksi.php dengan perintah \"gedit lokomedia/config/koneksi.php\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/--12cVwX8QRE/U0TfDakUKVI/AAAAAAAABLM/Bpj4S3P4eXE/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:11:58.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/--12cVwX8QRE/U0TfDakUKVI/AAAAAAAABLM/Bpj4S3P4eXE/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:11:58.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>18 muncul jendela aplikasi gedit dan ganti username dengan username database password dengan password database dan juga nama database dengan nama database yang tadi anda buat kalo sudah save dan tutup lalu restart apache anda lagi <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8hopP4OWViE/U0TfI5ShFUI/AAAAAAAABLU/H-kJ6ZAPvaE/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:12:16.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8hopP4OWViE/U0TfI5ShFUI/AAAAAAAABLU/H-kJ6ZAPvaE/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:12:16.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>19.masuk ke browser buka tab baru masukan alamat \"localhost/lokomedia\" jika semua benar muncul seperti gambar untuk error dapat dicari di wesite resminya yaitu di <span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Website Resmi CMS lokomedia : <a href=\"http://bukulokomedia.com/\">http://bukulokomedia.com/</a></span></span><br /><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fjG8jW4qwxU/U0TfYEaX9hI/AAAAAAAABLc/KQDQCzBT4K8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:27:07.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fjG8jW4qwxU/U0TfYEaX9hI/AAAAAAAABLc/KQDQCzBT4K8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:27:07.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-72Wp_YliofE/U0TfdiZG94I/AAAAAAAABLo/ISAeQ1kq9Yk/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:27:46.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-72Wp_YliofE/U0TfdiZG94I/AAAAAAAABLo/ISAeQ1kq9Yk/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:27:46.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KFJOqMSuDIU/U0Tfm-etqXI/AAAAAAAABL8/5Hw_Dbih57Q/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:28:08.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KFJOqMSuDIU/U0Tfm-etqXI/AAAAAAAABL8/5Hw_Dbih57Q/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-10+12:28:08.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>', 'http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/04/install-cms-lokomedia-di-ubuntu-1204.html', 1),
(116, 'Cara Menambahkan Tema Moodle 26 dan mengantinya', '2014-04-08', 'Anda dapat Download Theme moodle disini<a href=\"https://moodle.org/plugins/browse.php?list=category&amp;id=3\" target=\"_blank\"> https://moodle.org/plugins/browse.php?list=category&amp;id=3&nbsp; </a>atau di <a href=\"http://moodle.org/\">moodle.org</a><br /><br /><br /><br />1.masuk ke moodle di browser dengan memasukan \"ipserver/moodle/\" atau \"localhost/moodle\" atau disesuaikan dengan tempat anda install setelah masuk moodle login sebagai admin <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vaBJkq_JAB8/U0PAGQgPGWI/AAAAAAAABGk/YKVYDJTJN_E/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:15:37.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vaBJkq_JAB8/U0PAGQgPGWI/AAAAAAAABGk/YKVYDJTJN_E/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:15:37.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-w1Sd0ef-OCw/U0PAGLWg4UI/AAAAAAAABGc/AJIvqWErtDk/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:15:46.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-w1Sd0ef-OCw/U0PAGLWg4UI/AAAAAAAABGc/AJIvqWErtDk/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:15:46.png\" height=\"179\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>2.setelah masuk sabagai admin masuk ke Site administrator =&gt; plugin =&gt; install add-ons sesuai gambar<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SUjtMHkLuTc/U0PAGV9LF9I/AAAAAAAABGg/vwHMK2gEeLY/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:16:24.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SUjtMHkLuTc/U0PAGV9LF9I/AAAAAAAABGg/vwHMK2gEeLY/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:16:24.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>3.silahkan isi choose ganti dengan pilihan Themes dan choose a file upload pilih file thema moodle yang anda download tadi jika themes folder tidak writetable silahkan masukan perintah di terminal \"chmod 777 /var/www/moodle/theme\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9GFvSLLCpRk/U0PAHG9IGlI/AAAAAAAABG0/MLv6HoXM0v4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:16:38.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9GFvSLLCpRk/U0PAHG9IGlI/AAAAAAAABG0/MLv6HoXM0v4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:16:38.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-H-EVk1WcXFw/U0PAHagIetI/AAAAAAAABG4/HSAU5inYroA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:17:20.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-H-EVk1WcXFw/U0PAHagIetI/AAAAAAAABG4/HSAU5inYroA/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:17:20.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>4.gambar dibawah menunjukan folder sudah write table<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OMGDKhzKH40/U0PAH_WykPI/AAAAAAAABHA/nPSWC5MOYO0/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:17:39.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OMGDKhzKH40/U0PAH_WykPI/AAAAAAAABHA/nPSWC5MOYO0/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:17:39.png\" height=\"359\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>5.pilih han choose a file tadi sesusai gambar:<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-86SgiivUWKU/U0PAIUCqopI/AAAAAAAABHE/8eqB1oOhyYc/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-08+16:17:48.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\