(117, 'Mengistall moodle 2.6 di ubuntu 12.04', '2014-04-07', 'Cara Install moodle yaitu pertama pastikan anda sudah download file nya di situs resmi yaitu di <span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"hps\"><a href=\"http://download.moodle.org/\">http://download.moodle.org/</a> </span></span>baca juga <a href=\"http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/04/sedikit-tentang-moodle.html\">http://ajikamaludin.blogspot.com/2014/04/sedikit-tentang-moodle.html</a><br /><br /><br /><br />Langkah-langkah mengistall Moodle:<br />1.masuk terminal dan masuk sebagai root dengan perintah \"sudo su\" <br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZhjjI7bOw1k/U0KAmBtpGwI/AAAAAAAABCs/wH4EiR5ffM8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:22:51.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZhjjI7bOw1k/U0KAmBtpGwI/AAAAAAAABCs/wH4EiR5ffM8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:22:51.png\" height=\"356\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>2.pindahkan file yang anda download ke /var/www dengan perintah \"mv moodle-latest-26.zip /var/www/\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-I3CsIc_qdB4/U0KAl0glJCI/AAAAAAAABCo/rDiI_NANvig/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:23:52.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-I3CsIc_qdB4/U0KAl0glJCI/AAAAAAAABCo/rDiI_NANvig/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:23:52.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>3.silahkan and apindah direktori ke /var/www dengan perintah \"cd /var/www/<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-jBpvwkVH3T0/U0KAmbX5S-I/AAAAAAAABCw/t-WlEzsZKgg/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:24:05.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-jBpvwkVH3T0/U0KAmbX5S-I/AAAAAAAABCw/t-WlEzsZKgg/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:24:05.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>4. ekstrak file yang anda download dengan perintah \"unzip moodle-letest-26.zip\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-n5ODgRCqAC8/U0KAoHRo6yI/AAAAAAAABDA/w4QwhZu7SH4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:24:18.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-n5ODgRCqAC8/U0KAoHRo6yI/AAAAAAAABDA/w4QwhZu7SH4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:24:18.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-k9C3cp_MCF4/U0KApC5TZPI/AAAAAAAABDI/ugDO286lxEo/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:24:37.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-k9C3cp_MCF4/U0KApC5TZPI/AAAAAAAABDI/ugDO286lxEo/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:24:37.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>4.buat folder moodledata di folder /var/ folder ini diminta dari moodle langsung harus dibuat manual dengan memasukan perintah \"mkdir /var/moodledata\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-x4-WIFzCiBY/U0KApM-eJVI/AAAAAAAABDE/4F29dtOl004/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:24:56.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-x4-WIFzCiBY/U0KApM-eJVI/AAAAAAAABDE/4F29dtOl004/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-07+17:24:56.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>5.berikan hak akses pada moodledata dengan perintah \"chmod 777 /var/moodledata\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-iqUJUi_5rVU/U0KAp0yZvoI/AAAAAAAABDQ/1jorZqXda6