sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"hps\">PHP</span> <span class=\"hps\">Data Objects</span> <span class=\"hps\">modul</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">diinstal (</span>http://www.php.net/pdo) <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"hps\">Modul</span> <span class=\"hps\">PDO_MySQL</span> <span class=\"hps\">harus diaktifkan</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">(</span><span class=\"\">http://www.php.net/manual/en/ref.pdo- mysql.php</span>) <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"hps\">GD</span> <span class=\"hps\">versi 2.0</span> <span class=\"hps\">atau</span> <span class=\"hps\">yang lebih baru</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">(</span>opsional, <span class=\"hps\">tetapi</span> <span class=\"hps\">diperlukan untuk</span> <span class=\"hps\">profil</span> <span class=\"hps\">gambar</span>) <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"hps\">Curl</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">(</span><span class=\"\">untuk memungkinkan</span> <span class=\"hps\">Plugin</span> <span class=\"hps\">sandboxing</span>) <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"hps\">MySQL</span> <span class=\"hps\">5</span> <span class=\"hps\">atau</span> <span class=\"hps\">yang lebih baru</span> <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"hps\">Apache</span> <span class=\"hps\">2</span> <span class=\"hps\">atau</span> <span class=\"hps\">yang lebih baru</span> <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"hps\">AllowOverride</span> <span class=\"hps\">=</span> <span class=\"hps\">Semua</span> <span class=\"hps\">(opsional</span>, <span class=\"hps\">tetapi memungkinkan</span> <span class=\"hps\">url</span> <span class=\"hps\">ramah</span>) <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"hps\">mod_rewrite</span> <span class=\"hps atn\">(</span><span class=\"\">opsional</span>, <span class=\"hps\">tetapi memungkinkan</span> <span class=\"hps\">url</span> <span class=\"hps\">ramah</span>) <br /><span class=\"hps\">-Persyaratan</span> <span class=\"hps\">Browser</span> <br /><span class=\"hps\"></span><span class=\"hps\">javascript</span> <span class=\"hps\">library</span> <span class=\"hps\">yang kita gunakan adalah</span> <span class=\"hps\">jQuery</span>, <span class=\"hps\">jadi kami</span> <span class=\"hps\">sesuai dengan persyaratan</span> <span class=\"hps\">browser mereka</span><span class=\"\">.</span> <span class=\"hps\">Perlu dicatat</span>, <span class=\"hps\">bagaimanapun, bahwa</span> <span class=\"hps\">semua halaman</span> <span class=\"hps\">di</span> <span class=\"hps\">Vanilla</span> <span class=\"hps\">tetap</span> <span class=\"hps\">berfungsi penuh</span> <span class=\"hps\">dengan</span> <span class=\"hps\">javascript</span> <span class=\"hps\">dimatikan sepenuhnya</span><span class=\"\">.</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><br /><br /><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"\">Langkah-Langkah mengistall Vanilla :</span></span><br /><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"\">1.pastikan anda sudah download vanilla ,masuk terminal dan masuk sebagai root&nbsp; dengan perintah \"sudo su\" </span></span><br /><span class=\"\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"id\"><span class=\"\">&nbsp;</span> </span><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-w6vW3YvOG-8/Uz0zQZV2qmI/AAAAAAAAA_g/Jzgns_F38d8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-03+17:01:04.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-w6vW3YvOG-8/Uz0zQZV2qmI/AAAAAAAAA_g/Jzgns_F38d8/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-03+17:01:04.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SiHoUeMW6bM/Uz0zQ9a8S2I/AAAAAAAAA_s/LM0x8JWdXU4/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-03+17:01:26.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1e