(125, 'Mengistall Efront di Ubuntu 12.04', '2014-04-01', '<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"long_text\" id=\"result_box\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"eFront is a modern learning and training platform designed to help create online learning communities with opportunities for rich interaction.\">eFront  adalah aplikasi web server berupa alat belajar yang modern dan platform pelatihan yang dirancang untuk  membantu menciptakan komunitas belajar online dengan kesempatan untuk  berinteraksi. </span><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"It comes with a distinctive icon-based user interface that is intuitive to use.\">Muncul dengan berbasis icon user interface khas yang intuitif untuk digunakan. </span><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"The platform offers a wide range of features from content creation , test builder, project management , extended statistics , many communication tools, payments support , social extensions and more.\">Platform  ini menawarkan berbagai fitur dari penciptaan konten, uji pembangun,  manajemen proyek, statistik diperpanjang, banyak alat komunikasi,  pembayaran dukungan, ekstensi sosial dan banyak lagi. </span><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"It is a SCORM 1.2 and SCORM 2004/ 4th edition compliant and certified system.\">Ini adalah SCORM 1.2 dan SCORM 2004 / 4th edition sistem compliant dan bersertifikat. </span><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"eFront is a multilingual platform offered in 40+ languages. &lt;br&gt;\">eFront adalah platform multibahasa ditawarkan dalam 40 + bahasa. </span><span style=\"background-color: white;\" title=\"Several features of the platform (eg, skills management , organization structure , supervisor role) make it especially suitable for inner organization usage , especially at training or human resource management departments.\">Beberapa  fitur dari platform (misalnya, keterampilan manajemen, struktur  organisasi, peran pengawas) membuatnya sangat cocok untuk penggunaan  organisasi batin, terutama pada pelatihan atau sumber daya manusia  departemen manajemen.</span></span></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><br /></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Download Efront : &nbsp;</span></span><br /><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><a href=\"http://www.efrontlearning.net/download\">http://www.efrontlearning.net/download</a> /</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><a href=\"http://sourceforge.net/projects/efrontlearning/files/efrontlearning/\" target=\"_blank\">http://sourceforge.net/projects/efrontlearning/files/efrontlearning/&nbsp;</a></span></span></li></ul><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Download modules : <a href=\"http://www.efrontlearning.net/mods\">http://www.efrontlearning.net/mods</a></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Website Resmi : <a href=\"http://www.efrontlearning.net/\">http://www.efrontlearning.net/</a></span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">pastikan sudah terinstall aplikasi berikut jika belum silahkan install:</span></span><br /><br />apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client<br />apt-get install apache2<br />apt-get install php5 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><br /></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><br /></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Langkah-Langkah Mengistall Efront:</span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">1.Masuk ke terminal dan masuk sebagai root dengan perintah \"sudo su\"</span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">&nbsp;pastikan file efront sudah di download </span></span><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-77Sz9xNyWHQ/UzvIEE3y_-I/AAAAAAAAA80/HtgnIu3rfL0/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-02+12:36:10.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-77Sz9xNyWHQ/UzvIEE3y_-I/AAAAAAAAA80/HtgnIu3rfL0/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-02+12:36:10.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></span></span></div><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><br /></span></span><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZKSxDL-sxmk/UzvIEi4wtqI/AAAAAAAAA8s/vx7fyUjERUI/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-02+12:36:22.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZKSxDL-sxmk/UzvIEi4wtqI/AAAAAAAAA8s/vx7fyUjERUI/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-04-02+12:36:22.png\" height=\"358\" width=\"640\" /></a></span></span></div><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">2.pindahkan file efront ke folder /var/www/ dengan perintah \"mv efront_3.6.14_build18016_community.zip /var/www/\"</span></span><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: