=\"384\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>6. file sudah anda silahkan langsung ekstrak isi file didalam nya dengan perintah \"unzip Joomla_3.2.2-Stable-Full_package.zip\"<br />7.lalu jika sudah benar semua masukan perintah \"chmod 755 Joomla\"<br />8.kemudian masuk ke Browser masukan alamat \"localhost/phpmyadmin\"<br />pass = sesuai komputer anda lalu klik \"Go\"<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0sQgNp4L1q0/Ux6n1gu4JMI/AAAAAAAAAXY/U0NZpxB3pJI/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-03-11+13:05:41.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0sQgNp4L1q0/Ux6n1gu4JMI/AAAAAAAAAXY/U0NZpxB3pJI/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-03-11+13:05:41.png\" height=\"215\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>9.lalu muncul tampilan seperti dibawah klik&nbsp; Database<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XLCLqlyN-b8/Ux6ohs0fTRI/AAAAAAAAAXk/FMajcjRHtGM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-03-11+13:07:12.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XLCLqlyN-b8/Ux6ohs0fTRI/AAAAAAAAAXk/FMajcjRHtGM/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-03-11+13:07:12.png\" height=\"176\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-YX5jeVOgwN8/Ux6ohT-dg9I/AAAAAAAAAXg/Ajw0Gicv9W0/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-03-11+13:07:45.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-YX5jeVOgwN8/Ux6ohT-dg9I/AAAAAAAAAXg/Ajw0Gicv9W0/s1600/Screenshot+from+2014-03-11+13:07:45.png\" height=\"112\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>&nbsp;10.Buat database anda dan pastikan database anda ada di dalamnya<br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-spUSC_ouBYA/Ux6ohtItF3I/AAAAA